strings: <voice_0x0100107E><se_low>*: ...Hm?

<voice_0x0100107F><se_low>*: I say, someone other than Tom for once!
The old boy doesn't often let people in,
you know!

<voice_0x01001080><se_low>*: You've caught me at a rather busy time,
I'm afraid. I'll be with you in a jiffy.

<voice_0x01001084><se_low>*: There!
I think I'll take a breather for a while.
Sorry to keep you waiting.

<voice_0x01001085><se_low>*: So, you're an explorer, eh!?
I'm Felix.

<voice_0x01001086><se_low>Felix: ...Well, well!
Tom's really got an eye for people!
Only lets decent chaps through, you know!

<voice_0x01001087><se_low>Felix: Yes... You might just be able to assist me.
There's a little undertaking I need some help with. Allow me to explain...

<voice_0x01001088><se_low>Felix: It's an old chum of mine, you see.
Gone and got himself lost, would you believe.
<voice_0x01001089><se_low>Felix: Normally I'd go and help the old bean out myself of course, but as you can see, I've got a lot on my plate just at the mo.

<voice_0x0100108A><se_low>Felix: That's where you come in. I'd like you to go
and give the old bean a bit of assistance.
If you don't mind, that is...
<voice_0x0100108B><se_low>Felix: Well? What do you say? Will you help?

<voice_0x0100108C><se_low>Felix: I see... Well, that's a bally shame.
I suppose I'll just have to go and do it myself.

<voice_0x0100108D><se_low>Felix: I can't force you, what.
Take care, then!
Chin up, and all that!

<voice_0x0100108E><se_low>Felix: Capital!
Right, I'll tell you what you need to do, then.
<voice_0x0100108F><se_low>Felix: Around these parts, there are four great sabrecat statues. You might have seen one of them on your way over here.

<voice_0x01001090><se_low>Felix: They all point to the same place. There's a strange tree there that's only visible at dawn. And that's precisely where the old chap is,
you see.

<voice_0x01001091><se_low>Felix: All I need you to do is go there and
give him this.
<Cap><leader> receives some sand of serenity and puts it in the bag.

<voice_0x01001092><se_low>Felix: He's a clever old bean.
Just give him that and he'll know what to do.
<voice_0x01001093><se_low>Felix: Once you've given it to him, come back and pay me a visit. I'll have a little token of appreciation for you.

<voice_0x01001094><se_low>Felix: If you leave here and head up the hill you'll
get a view of a couple of the sabrecat statues.
It's worth taking a look before you go off exploring!
<voice_0x01001095>Felix: Ah!
<voice_0x01001096><se_low>Felix: Golly! I nearly forgot!

<voice_0x01001097><se_low>Felix: I suppose you've never ridden a great sabrecat before, eh? Well, this'll be a fine chance!
Speak to Tom. He'll give you what you need.

<voice_0x01001098><se_low>Felix: Give the old speed a bit of a boost, what!
Tom will explain the rest.

<voice_0x0100109C><se_low>Felix: Eh? Oh, I say! You again!
Had a change of heart?
You'd like to help now, would you?

<voice_0x0100109D><se_low>Felix: No?
Then please be kind enough not to disturb me!
I've got things to do, hm!
